---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | DGSDK"
  description="Privacy Policy of DGSDK – Dongguan Shidike Automation Equipment Co., Ltd. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your personal information."
  noLangAlternates={true}
>
  <section class="privacy-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p>Last updated: April 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="privacy-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="privacy-body">

        <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>
          Dongguan Shidike Automation Equipment Co., Ltd. ("DGSDK", "we", "us", or "our") operates
          the website <a href="https://www.dg-sdk.com">www.dg-sdk.com</a>. This Privacy Policy explains
          how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website or
          contact us for business inquiries.
        </p>

        <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We may collect the following types of information:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Contact information</strong> – name, email address, phone number, company name, and country, when you submit an inquiry or contact form.</li>
          <li><strong>Usage data</strong> – IP address, browser type, pages visited, and time spent on pages, collected automatically through analytics tools (Vercel Analytics).</li>
          <li><strong>Communication records</strong> – messages you send us via email, WhatsApp, or our contact forms.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Respond to your product inquiries and provide quotations</li>
          <li>Send order confirmations, invoices, and shipping updates</li>
          <li>Improve the content and functionality of our website</li>
          <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal information to third parties for marketing purposes.</p>

        <h2>4. Cookies and Analytics</h2>
        <p>
          Our website uses Vercel Analytics and Speed Insights to understand how visitors interact with
          our site. These tools may collect anonymized usage data. You can disable cookies in your
          browser settings at any time.
        </p>

        <h2>5. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>
          We retain your personal information only as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined
          in this policy, or as required by applicable law. Inquiry and order records are typically
          retained for up to 5 years for business record purposes.
        </p>

        <h2>6. Data Security</h2>
        <p>
          We implement reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect your personal
          information from unauthorized access, disclosure, or loss. However, no method of transmission
          over the Internet is 100% secure.
        </p>

        <h2>7. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>Our website may use the following third-party services:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Formspree</strong> – for processing contact form submissions</li>
          <li><strong>Vercel</strong> – for website hosting and analytics</li>
          <li><strong>WhatsApp / Email</strong> – for direct business communication</li>
        </ul>
        <p>These services have their own privacy policies, which we encourage you to review.</p>

        <h2>8. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>Depending on your location, you may have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
          <li>Request correction or deletion of your data</li>
          <li>Object to or restrict certain processing of your data</li>
        </ul>
        <p>To exercise these rights, please contact us at the address below.</p>

        <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Company:</strong> Dongguan Shidike Automation Equipment Co., Ltd.</li>
          <li><strong>Email:</strong> dgsdk2013@gmail.com</li>
          <li><strong>Phone:</strong> +86 13602342003</li>
          <li><strong>Address:</strong> Binhai Road 33, Dongguan, Guangdong, China</li>
        </ul>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .privacy-hero {
      padding: 120px 0 48px;
      background: #f7f8fa;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #ececec;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .privacy-hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #111;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .privacy-hero p {
      color: #888;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .privacy-content {
      padding: 64px 0 96px;
      background: #fff;
    }

    .privacy-body {
      max-width: 780px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .privacy-body h2 {
      font-size: 1.35rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #111;
      margin: 40px 0 14px;
    }

    .privacy-body p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.85;
      color: #555;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .privacy-body ul {
      padding-left: 22px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .privacy-body ul li {
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.85;
      color: #555;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .privacy-body a {
      color: #0071e3;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .privacy-body a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .privacy-hero {
        padding: 100px 0 36px;
      }

      .privacy-content {
        padding: 40px 0 64px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
